Nothing more important than her child is, so she is a mother; Laxmi. Then She is also having in one hand, another like this – see Laxmi? She gives you “abhaya”, She gives you reassurance – abhaya. And this which She gives. So the man who is supposed to be rich must have must people whom he has given some assurances. To whom they are “ashritas”. Dependents.

